game.description:
Are you ready to play out your reckless desires? If yes, join immediately this brand new car game and get ready to live your intense racing craving. Stunts Track is an exclusively-designed 3D racing game in which you have to put your driving skill to challenge. The victory will only be yours if you dare to make awesome stunts and death-defying tricks. This supercar is sure to give you those fun hours you want to experience in a free online car game. 

Complete different types of tricks and maneuvers and get a chance to become a racing pro! Start your game by visiting the training ground in this fun car game! You will surely see yourself enjoying fun physics within short gameplay. Come forward and take charge of a lovely car! It?s the you who have to make the flips, jump on the ramps, turn forward and backward! Don?t forget to attempt the slalom between the cones to create the goosebumps in your body!

The job is pretty difficult, but you can finish it by just flying your car through 3 circles on its all four wheels. Apply your intense driving and concentration skills to get the job done fast in this one of the best HTML5 games for kids! Trust me; lots of freedom to explore for you in this new driving simulator! Do whatever you want to do since this cool fun mobile game has no limits! You are sure to enjoy a lot in this easy-to-control game.
